  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top: 3.35pt;\u0022\u003EJoin Douglas Johnson, ATC as he continues the third of four webinars focused expressly on understanding the clinical application of super pulsed laser and light treatment (SPLT).\u0026nbsp; This month we will discuss methods of treatment and how they improve outcomes.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Under pressure\u0026hellip;how to reduce swelling in the upper and lower extremities\u003Cbr /\u003E\n*Hot flash\u0026hellip;eliminating inflammation to accelerate healing\u003Cbr /\u003E\n*Pain in the\u0026hellip;how best to deal with acute and chronic pain\u003Cbr /\u003E\n*Cramp\u0026hellip;how to deactivate trigger points and ease muscle spasms\u003Cbr /\u003E\n*Quick Start: Getting Success from Day 1 using basic methods\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
